REMAINING SETUP:
================

 * In order to Finish your Drupal setup, you will need to 
   define a new mysql root password with the folloing command:
   'mysqladmin -u root password NEW_PASSWORD'

 * (Optional) You can also setup the ServerName/Serveralias directives 
   located in apache2 configuration (file /etc/apache2/sites-enabled/wordpress)

